          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this class to specify matching criteria to filter all of the discoverable devices connected to the system into devices of interest. This is the main method of receiving a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.CoreHID/documentation/CoreHID/HIDDeviceClient/DeviceReference-swift.struct",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " used to create a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.CoreHID/documentation/CoreHID/HIDDeviceClient",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Matching criteria are specified by creating ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.CoreHID/documentation/CoreHID/HIDDeviceManager/DeviceMatchingCriteria",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and passing them to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.CoreHID/documentation/CoreHID/HIDDeviceManager/monitorNotifications(matchingCriteria:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". References to devices that match the criteria are received using ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.CoreHID/documentation/CoreHID/HIDDeviceManager/Notification/deviceMatched(_:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " notifications.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
